    {
      "number": 2,
      "id": "PR_kwDON3ePec7l71oy",
      "title": "Fix incorrect RFC reference (RFC7264 to RFC7624) in Introduction",
      "url": "https://github.com/ietf-wg-mops/draft-ietf-mops-network-overlay-impacts/pull/2",
      "state": "MERGED",
      "author": "smishra1200",
      "authorAssociation": "COLLABORATOR",
      "assignees": [],
      "labels": [],
      "body": "Corrects an incorrect reference in the Introduction flagged by David Schinazi in his review of -03.\n\nThe Introduction cited RFC7264 in two places where it should be RFC7624 (\"Confidentiality in the Face of Pervasive Surveillance\"), which is the RFC that explored the threats from RFC7258 and outlined mitigations. Section 2 already uses RFC7624 correctly, so this brings the Introduction in line.\n\nNo other changes (grammar and editorial items from the review will follow separately).\n",
      "createdAt": "2026-06-12T21:35:05Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-12T21:45:01Z",
      "baseRepository": "ietf-wg-mops/draft-ietf-mops-network-overlay-impacts",
